---
title: "invalidateOrders (GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_loop: for each orderUid
    q_loop --> q_invalidate: gpV2Settlement.invalidateOrder(orderUid)
    q_invalidate --> q_loop: order invalidated
    q_loop --> [*]: all orders invalidated

    note right of q_invalidate
        INV-001: Caller must have ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE
        INV-002: Delegates to GPv2Settlement for actual order cancellation
    end note
